      "content": "it's just... the way you put it. \"stop fighting.\" it sounds almost peaceful, which is what's scaring me. like, if she just accepts it, the fear goes away? but it also feels like she's just giving up on everything she was meant to be. is it really \"honest\" to just let it all go?",
